      *              * Incremento contatore                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-ctr-prg-ctw          .
       rou-let-reg-fun-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     rou-let-reg-fun-200.
       rou-let-reg-fun-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     rou-let-reg-fun-999.
       rou-let-reg-fun-999.
           exit.

