      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sistema applicativo                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      i-ide-sap            to   r-ide-sis-app          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Area gestionale                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      i-ide-arg            to   r-ide-are-ges          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Settore gestionale                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      i-ide-set            to   r-ide-set-ges          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fase gestionale                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      i-ide-fas            to   r-ide-fas-ges          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Informazioni da preparazione param. stampa  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
